svg.metadata: Created by FontForge 20120731 at Sun Sep 1 03:56:33 2013 By Stefan Warting The font was prepared to the bicentennial anniversary of famous Russian writer Nikolai Gogol. It is based on original writings from Gogol's letters and from the drafts to the second chapter of "Mertvye Dushi" novel. Designer - Gennady Fridman. Released by ParaType April 1, 2009.
